    <li>Delete your email address from our database.</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise these rights, please contact us at [Contact Information].</p>

<p><strong>Changes to This Privacy Policy</strong></p>
<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by sending an email to the address you have provided.</p>
